{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"150a6767fc","title":"关于应对国民党军火力袭击的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"dbb2502d55","index":0,"year":1958,"month":6,"day":26,"articleId":"150a6767fc"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji39","name":"毛泽东全集第39卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/39-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji39":{"comments":[{"id":"91cd9b6b45","publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"150a6767fc","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是毛泽东在中共中央军委委员、国务院副总理兼国防部部长彭德怀1958年6月26日星送的电话记录上写的批语。"},{"id":"832c574e32","publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"150a6767fc","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"中国人民解放军总参谋部作战部1958年6月26日上午电话报告：福州军区判断，国民党军最近可能对我组织一次大的火力袭击。据此，福州军区提出两项应对措施。一是消极方面的，采取撤离等防范措施，高炮加强对空作战。二为积极方面的，即组织还击。总参谋长票裕指示：除火炮防敌袭击外，另调一些高射炮部队，集中火力打击故飞机。如有机会再打地面目标，并同意作战部关于积极进行还击准备，待敌暴露目标后很狠给敌以打击的建议。彭德怀6月26日12时批示：“即送主席阅后审批。我同意第二项措施，采取积极还击并加强对空火力。”"}],"contents":[{"id":"55ae757095","type":"title","text":"关于应对国民党军火力袭击的批语则","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"150a6767fc"},{"id":"91cd9b6b45","type":"subtitle","text":"退彭照办”。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"150a6767fc"},{"id":"832c574e32","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"150a6767fc"},{"id":"cb5c924d6c","type":"paragraph","text":"六月二十六日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"150a6767fc"}],"page":{"id":"99acdde077","publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"150a6767fc","start":441,"end":441}}}},"__N_SSG":true}